{"word":"μάργος","slug":"μάργος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μάργος</b></el> <el>(μάργος, η, ον) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>raging mad</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>furiosus</el>, <el>μάργε</el>, <i>madman!</i> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; then in <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of appetite, <i>greedy, gluttonous</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>lewd, lustful</i>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}